Lame version 3.98
Software Homepage: http://lame.sourceforge.net/index.php
Source Download URL: http://downloads.sourceforge.net/lame/lame-398.tar.gz
Notes:
Lame 3.98.2 doesn't work with FFMPEG as of FFMPEG revision 16686; neither
 FFMPEG nor Lame seem to be in a hurry to fix, so we use lame 3.98 which
 does work.

